Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:54.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}それでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:02:00.89,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}頼りない武装でも　君を救って行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:10.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}思い出せないほどに　時が経つまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:12.97,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Far  away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:13.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Find  the  way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.78,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Fly  Fafnir
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.30,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}才能も超えて上昇する！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:22.41,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君にはその瞳があるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.01,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ねぇ　見据えていて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:28.24,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}選ばれた運命を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:33.88,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}生き抜くたび　隣にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:35.96,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}構え
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.93,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}矢を放て
