Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:13.57,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an2}Find  the  way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.78,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3\an2}Fly  Fafnir
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.30,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}超越才能向上攀爬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:22.41,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}用你的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.01,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}去看清所有
